snippet.title: Mushroom Picnic Party Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Mushroom Picnic Party is a hidden object game where you help Townsfolk find all the lost little mushrooms and prepare for a picnic party!

Guests from far away will attend the party, and you want to make the best impression possible!

Wishlist now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2469280/Mushroom_Picnic_Party/
